Template Ref
-handle on a Dom Element
grap elemenet and manipulate

refrence to a dom elemen inside a variable 

Exaple we astablick a connection reffrence between a button and an input field throuh pur ref element

<input type="text" ref="name">
<button @click="handleClick">click me</button>

 methods: {
    handleClick() {
      console.log(this.$refs.name)
    }
  }





Side notes:

add a class JS
this.$refs.name.classList.add("active")
